rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex-sama,
How was it returning
to your hometown after so long?

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0002
rows.name:
The kids have really grown up, but
the village itself hasn't changed much.
It felt really familiar.

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm totally rested and ready to go!
I'll lead you all the way to the port!

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0005
rows.name:
hough to be honest...
The port is actually on
the next island over.

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0006
rows.name: It's not far, so let's get going.
